  "title": "Senior Staff Nurse [Central]",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 440938]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver safe, competent, and individualised nursing care based on patient needs.</li><li>Maintain nursing standards in documentation, treatment, monitoring, and infection control.</li><li>Manage and allocate medical equipment and consumables efficiently.</li><li>Communicate effectively with patients, families, caregivers, and care teams.</li><li>Coordinate patient care with physicians and support multidisciplinary collaboration.</li><li>Comply with protocols for drug and medical supply storage and implement safety measures.</li><li>Document patient conditions, referrals, and interventions accurately.</li><li>Monitor patient progress to support care planning and family coping.</li><li>Administer medications and perform wound care.</li><li>Ensure continuity of care through follow‑up on treatment plans.</li><li>Maintain a safe, organised, and confidential patient care environment.</li><li>Mentor junior staff and support their development.</li><li>Ensure compliance with Singapore Nursing Board standards and industry guidelines.</li><li>Uphold housekeeping standards and contribute to continuous improvement.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Registered Nurse with the Singapore Nursing Board.</strong></li><li><strong>Minimum 3 years of experience in general nursing care.</strong></li><li>Experience in hospital or hospice settings is an added advantage.</li><li>Exposure to Oncology, Palliative Care, Geriatrics, or Gerontology disciplines is an added advantage.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
